      "rationale": "Independent review conducted by FDA CDRH computational scientist (not part of development team). Review checklist covered geometry import, material assignment, boundary condition application, and load application. Two minor discrepancies identified and corrected prior to final analysis. Review sign-off documented in Review Record USE-001."
