      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum mechanics formulation with nonlinear geometry and bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity appropriate for Ti-6Al-4V; contact formulation captures screw-rod and screw-vertebral body block interfaces.",
      "rationale": "Large-deformation formulation (NLGEOM ON) with bilinear isotropic hardening (E_t = 1.1 GPa, σ_y = 880 MPa per coupon testing). Augmented Lagrange contact at screw-rod and rod-block interfaces. Model form validated against three independent FEA implementations (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes); inter-model QoI spread <3%. Model form uncertainty assessed as low."
    },
