      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and yield strength from 12-specimen coupon tensile testing (mean E = 113.4 GPa, CV = 1.8%). Geometry from CMM measurements of each of the 11 test constructs (individual-specimen models). Friction coefficient μ = 0.15 ± 0.05 (literature range); sensitivity to friction documented in validation report Section 5. Input uncertainty propagated via LHS UQ campaign (500 samples)."
