      "rationale": "N=11 constructs from three production lots (4+4+3 split). All constructs dimensionally verified by CMM; all within drawing tolerances. Material certification records (mill certificates, heat treatment records) obtained and archived. Sample size sufficient for statistical comparison per ASME V&V 40 guidance."
    },
    {
