      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the range of COU loading scenarios; at least two load configurations or two displacement rates evaluated.",
      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single load configuration (ASTM F1717 standard compression-bending geometry) and single crosshead displacement rate (5 mm/min). Only one test condition evaluated, achieving Gradation 2 rather than the required Gradation 3. This factor is below required level and is documented as a gap; the limitation is accepted on the basis that ASTM F1717 represents the regulatory standard configuration and the COU is limited to this specific loading scenario. Risk accepted by the credibility assessment team."
    },
